msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Nīvaraṇavagga "
msgstr "4. Hindrances "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 37. Buddhisutta → vuddhi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Buddhisutta "
msgstr "37. Growth "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: buddhiyā → vuḍḍhiyā (s1-3) | vuddhiyā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.37:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā buddhiyā aparihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they lead to growth and progress. "

msgctxt "sn46.37:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.37:1.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo. "
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.37:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā buddhiyā aparihānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "When these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they lead to growth and progress.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.37:1.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

